## Build outputs (ignore DLL/LIB from build, but NOT from lib/)
Build/
Release/
Debug/
x64/
x86/

## Allow native libraries in lib/ (FFTW, SharpDX, SkiaSharp, etc.)
!Project Files/lib/**/*.dll
!Project Files/lib/**/*.lib
!Project Files/lib/**/*.exp

